<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Skincare Reminder - Kilifonia Beauty</title>

<style>

body{
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
margin:0;
padding:0;
background: linear-gradient(135deg,#667eea,#764ba2);
color:#333;
}

.container{
max-width:600px;
margin:0 auto;
background:white;
border-radius:20px;
overflow:hidden;
box-shadow:0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
}

/* HEADER */

.header{
background: linear-gradient(135deg,#f093fb,#f5576c);
color:white;
padding:40px 30px;
text-align:center;
}

.logo{
max-width:180px;
border-radius:12px;
box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
}

.brand-name{
font-size:28px;
font-weight:bold;
margin-top:15px;
}

.brand-tagline{
font-size:14px;
opacity:.9;
}

/* CONTENT */

.content{
padding:40px 35px;
}

.reminder-card{
background: linear-gradient(135deg,#f8f9fa,#e9ecef);
border-radius:15px;
padding:25px;
margin:25px 0;
border-left:5px solid #667eea;
box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
}

.routine-time{
font-size:20px;
font-weight:bold;
color:#667eea;
margin-bottom:12px;
}

.routine-tips{
background: linear-gradient(135deg,#e3f2fd,#bbdefb);
border-radius:12px;
padding:20px;
margin:20px 0;
border:1px solid #bbdefb;
}

.routine-tips h3{
color:#1976d2;
margin-top:0;
}

.routine-tips ul{
padding-left:20px;
}

.button{
display:inline-block;
background: linear-gradient(135deg,#667eea,#764ba2);
color:white;
padding:15px 35px;
border-radius:30px;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
margin:20px 0;
}

/* FOOTER */

.footer{
background: linear-gradient(135deg,#f8f9fa,#e9ecef);
padding:30px;
text-align:center;
font-size:13px;
color:#666;
border-top:1px solid #e0e0e0;
}

.social-links a{
color:#667eea;
margin:0 10px;
text-decoration:none;
}

/* RESPONSIVE */

@media(max-width:600px){

.container{
margin:10px;
}

.content{
padding:30px 25px;
}

.header{
padding:30px 20px;
}

.logo{
max-width:140px;
}

.brand-name{
font-size:24px;
}

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<!-- HEADER -->

<div class="header">

<img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dkdx7xytz/image/upload/v1772469610/blisslogo1_rwlktl.png"
class="logo"/>

<div class="brand-name">Kilifonia Beauty</div>
<div class="brand-tagline">Elevate Your Natural Beauty</div>

<h1 style="margin-top:20px">
<% if(timeOfDay === 'morning'){ %>
🌅 Morning Skincare Time!
<% } else { %>
🌙 Evening Skincare Time!
<% } %>
</h1>

<p>Your <%= timeOfDay %> self-care ritual awaits</p>

</div>

<!-- CONTENT -->

<div class="content">

<h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>

<p>
It's time for your
<strong style="color:#667eea"><%= routineType %> skincare routine</strong>.
Consistency is the secret to radiant skin and healthy glow.
</p>

<div class="reminder-card">

<div class="routine-time">
⏰ Scheduled Time: <%= scheduledTime %>
</div>

<p>
Your beautiful <strong><%= skinType %></strong> skin deserves this care moment.
Stay consistent for the best results.
</p>

</div>

<div class="routine-tips">

<h3>💡 Expert Tips for Your <%= routineType %> Routine</h3>

<ul>

<% if(routineType === 'AM'){ %>

<li>Gentle cleansing to start your day</li>
<li>Apply serum on damp skin</li>
<li>Always use SPF protection</li>
<li>Keep skin hydrated</li>

<% } else { %>

<li>Double cleanse before sleeping</li>
<li>Use active treatment products</li>
<li>Allow skin repair overnight</li>
<li>Apply nourishing oils</li>

<% } %>

</ul>

</div>

<div style="text-align:center">
<a href="https://kilifoniabeauty.co.ke/skincare-timetable"
class="button">
View Your Skincare Timetable
</a>
</div>

</div>

<!-- FOOTER -->

<div class="footer">

<p>
<strong>Kilifonia Beauty</strong><br>
Elevating Beauty Through Science and Nature
</p>

<div class="social-links">
<a href="https://kilifoniabeauty.co.ke">Website</a> •
<a href="https://instagram.com/kilifoniabeauty">Instagram</a> •
<a href="https://facebook.com/kilifoniabeauty">Facebook</a>
</div>

<p>
&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Kilifonia Beauty. All rights reserved.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>